 where <emphasis effect="italics">v</emphasis> is velocity, <emphasis effect="italics">d</emphasis> is the distance travelled, and <emphasis effect="italics">t</emphasis> is the time the object took to travel the distance. If the velocity-time data are plotted on a graph, which variable will be on which axis? Why?</para>
